ar but a believer, and none hates them but a hypocrite. Whoever loves them, Allah will love him. Whoever hates them, Allah will hate him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3783, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 75 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":665,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/31\/sweetness-faith-contentment\/","url_meta":{"origin":14726,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Sweetness of faith is satisfaction with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-'Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe has tasted the sweetness of faith who is content with Allah as a Lord, Islam as a religion, and Muhammad as a messenger.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 34 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/16\/love-for-muhammad-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":14726,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Until he loves me more than all people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2010","format":false,"excerpt"