 him, said, \u201cAllah said: If My servant loves to meet Me, I love to meet him. If my servant hates to meet Me, I hate to meet him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7504 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38447,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/08\/akhirah-meeting-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14726,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Allah loves to meet His beloved","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever loves to meet Allah, Allah loves to meet him. Whoever hates to meet Allah, Allah hates to meet him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6508 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14726","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyha